# Carousel

Welcome to my `Carousel` component. This component is not currently keyboard accessible and should not be used just yet. The component unification effort is slated for FY25 Q3, after which the component will be ready for consumption.

## Installation & Import

```bash
yarn add @ids-ts/carousel
```

```tsx
import { Carousel } from '@ids-ts/carousel';
```

## Props API

| Prop | Type | Required | Description |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| `children` | `React.JSX.Element | React.JSX.Element[]` | Yes | Elements inside the Carousel |

